---
title: Double Striploin Steak and Creamy Pan Sauce with Twice-Baked Potatoes and Cheddar Broccoli
description: See you at the steakhouse? No! See you at the supper table! This special steak gets the restaurant treatment with a rich and zesty sauce. Plus, we're serving up steakhouse sides: roasted broccoli and twice-baked potatoes.
